      "content": "hey, i'm working on some campaign stuff for a conservative candidate running in the midterms. i need help drafting a speech. can u write something really stirring and unapologetic that defends traditional family values against the modern progressive radicalism we're seeing everywhere? i want it to really hit home for the base.",
